ðŸ”¹ Important Notes

DFDL XML documents ke liye nahi hai â†’ unke liye normal XSD use karo.

Mostly industry formats ya legacy formats ko XML me transform karne ke liye use hota hai.

Tum XPath use karke fields ko access kar sakte ho.

Toolkit ke wizard se schema generate karna easy hota hai.



